    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Kept as a closely guarded secret by the deadly members of the Red Mantis assassins, this poison is treated with reverence for its ability to end lives. If the victim dies while affected by this poison, its body decomposes to nothing in 1 minute, leaving only its gear behind. Non-magical preservation can\u2019t protect the tainted corpse. *Peaceful rest* works on the poisoned body only if cast as a 5th-rank spell and the caster succeeds at a counteract check against the poison\u2019s saving throw DC when casting the spell. Even if cast successfully, peaceful rest only works as if it had been cast at 2nd rank.",
        "level": 20,
